summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 7, Block 1, West Woodland Park Addition, and Lot 3 and the South one-half of Lot 2, Block 24, Law's 2nd Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections to be numbered 2-46 and 17-29, respectively.
